{
  "name": "ecl_sigslots",
  "version": "1.2.1",
  "description": "Provides a signal/slot mechanism (in the same vein as qt sigslots,\n     boost::signals etc for intra-process communication. These include\n     some improvements - they do not need a preprocessor, are fully type safe,\n     allow for simple connections via a posix style string identifier\n     and are multithread-safe.",
